title: Middle of the Linked List
code:
# Definition for singly-linked list.
# class ListNode:
#     def __init__(self, val=0, next=None):
#         self.val = val
#         self.next = next
class Solution:
    def middleNode(self, head: Optional[ListNode]) -> Optional[ListNode]:

        midPnt = 0
        ptr = head
        while ptr != None:
            midPnt += 1
            ptr = ptr.next
        
        ptr = head
        for i in range(midPnt//2):
            ptr = ptr.next 
        
        return ptr

# Definition for singly-linked list.
# class ListNode:
#     def __init__(self, val=0, next=None):
#         self.val = val
#         self.next = next
class Solution:
    def getDecimalValue(self, head: ListNode) -> int:

        count = 0
        ptr = head

        while ptr != None:
            count = (count + ptr.val)*2
            ptr = ptr.next
        
        return count//2

class Solution(object):
    def plusOne(self, digits):
        """
        :type digits: List[int]
        :rtype: List[int]
        """
        carry = 0
        result = 0
        i = 1
        digits[-1] += 1
        
        while i< len(digits):
            if digits[-i] >9:
                digits[-i] = 0
                digits[-i-1] +=1
            i += 1
        
        if digits[-len(digits)] >9:
            digits[-len(digits)] = 0
            digits.insert(0,1)
            
        
        return digits

        j = 0

class Solution(object):
    def addTwoNumbers(self, l1, l2):
        """
        :type l1: ListNode
        :type l2: ListNode
        :rtype: ListNode
        """
        multiplier = 1
        num1 = 0
        num2 = 0
        num3 = 0
        
        while l1 or l2:
            if l1:
                num1 += l1.val*multiplier
                l1= l1.next
            if l2:
                num2 += l2.val*multiplier
                l2= l2.next
            multiplier *= 10
        
        multiplier = 10
        num3 +=  num1+num2
        
        head = ListNode(num3%multiplier)
        temp = head
        num3 = (num3-num3%multiplier)//multiplier
        
        while num3>0:
            temp.next = ListNode(num3%multiplier)
            temp = temp.next
            num3 = (num3-num3%multiplier)//multiplier
        
        return head
